Definition: a verb whose agent performs an action that is directed at the agent
Example: the sentence `he washed' has a reflexive verb; `perjure' is a reflexive verb because you cannot perjure anyone but yourself
Synonyms: verb, a, whose, agent, performs, an, action, that, is, directed, at, the, sentence, he, washed, has, reflexive, perjure, because, you, cannot, anyone, but, yourself
Category: noun.communication
